Package preibisch_imagej.table

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Column<T>
    A column of data of a Table.
    GenericTable
    A flexible table capable of storing any values as Objects.
    ResultsTable
    A table of double-precision floating point values.
    Table<C extends Column<T>,T>
    A table of values.
    TableDisplay
    Interface for Table Displays.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTable<C extends Column<T>,T>
    Abstract superclass for Table implementations.
    DefaultColumn<T>
    Default implementation of Column.
    DefaultGenericTable
    Default implementation of GenericTable.
    DefaultResultsTable
    Default implementation of ResultsTable.
    DefaultTableDisplay
    Default display for Tables, including ResultsTables.
    DoubleColumn
    Efficient implementation of Column for double primitives.
    GenericColumn
    A column that can consist of any Objects.
    ResultsImg
    Expresses a ResultsTable as an Img.
    TableLoader
    Loads a text file containing comma separated values into a ResultsTable.
